<i>For the following experiment,</i>

01:19:07.077 --> 01:19:09.412
<i>Silver received three different</i>
<i>models of still camera:</i>

01:19:09.496 --> 01:19:11.164
<i>a middle range</i>
<i>digital camera</i>

01:19:11.248 --> 01:19:12.832
<i>with a fixed /ens</i>
<i>focused on infinity,</i>

01:19:12.916 --> 01:19:15.043
<i>a conventional</i>
<i>analogical camera</i>

01:19:15.126 --> 01:19:17.337
<i>with a 50 mm /ens</i>
<i>focused on infinity</i>

