01:19:23.051 --> 01:19:25.178
<i>did not produce</i>
<i>any positive result'</i>

01:19:25.262 --> 01:19:27.973
<i>The second camera registered</i>
<i>only partial results,</i>

01:19:28.056 --> 01:19:30.350
<i>insufficient' for</i>
<i>a positive evaluation</i>

01:19:30.433 --> 01:19:33.687
<i>Only the Polaroid camera allowed</i>
<i>the apparent projection</i>

01:19:33.770 --> 01:19:35.897
<i>of Silver's thoughts</i>
